OL,5, The peer who organised the Queen's     
OL,6, funeral has been banned from driving   
OL,7, for six months, despite claiming he    
OL,8, needed his licence to arrange the      
OL,9, King's upcoming coronation.            
OL,11,FEdward Fitzalan-Howard, the 18th Duke  
OL,12,Fof Norfolk, was caught using his mobile
OL,13,Fphone while driving in Battersea,      
OL,14,Fsouth-west London, on 7 April.         
OL,16,FHe admitted the offence, at Lavender   
OL,17,FHill Magistrates' Court earlier.       
OL,19,FHe had hoped to avoid a ban by claiming
OL,20,F"exceptional hardship".                
